OL,3,CMan in hospital with gunshot wounds as
OL,4,Cfive arrested
OL,6,FFive people have been arrested
OL,7,Ffollowing a shooting in Gorse Hill,
OL,8,FSwindon, on Friday night
OL,10,FOfficers responded to reports of a
OL,11,Fgunshot being fired in St Paul's
OL,12,FStreet, Gorse Hill just before 9pm.
OL,14,FA man in his 30s was been taken to
OL,15,Fhospital with a suspected gunshot
OL,16,Fwound. His condition is described as
OL,17,Fserious but stable.
OL,19,FThe following remain in custody as
OL,20,Finquiries continue:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
